76561198193206533,Recommended,266390,16026733,"Posted: 27 May, 2015",all,cRaZy J,"This game is a well balanced combination of farming, Diner Dash, Zombies, and Tower defense. Plus a ridiculous element of Fruit ninja (but using a mouse for that is @$^#*$^#&)General:- Learn to maintain your farm with many different crops- Use your crops to cook dishes for people- Trade your cooked meals for vital materials to be used in crafting- craft tools to help the farm; use materials to expand the restaurant; use materials to trade for new seeds or other things; and create tower-defense type weapons to deflect the zombies- Day/ night cycles, where you can hire helpers during the day, and defend against zombies at night.- The zombies will take your produce, so use those weapons to deflect themGood stuff:-Awesome 3D cartoon style that operates smoothly.- Insanely fast loading when resuming the game (game takes a little while to load on first play)- Save mechanic is fantastic: easy and quick to use, and also has auto save.- always something to do. If there's some time to kill, then kill time by fast forwarding.Bad stuff:<<ERROR. NOT FOUND>>"
